These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-1::.
There 4 different types of food: blueberry, cranberry, kale, radish
1. the person eating blueberry is on the far left##1
2. the person eating cranberry is on the left or right of the person eating blueberry##3
3. the person eating cranberry is on the left or right of the person eating kale##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2     |  3   |   4    |
| Food   | blueberry | cranberry | kale | radish |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, fanta, iced-tea, water
1. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
2. the person drinking water is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
3. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage   | fanta | coffee | water | iced-tea |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, card-games, drawing, fishing
1. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
2. the person who's hobby is baking is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby   | baking | drawing | card-games | fishing |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, musical, spy, superhero
1. the person watching spy movies is on the far right##1
2. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1
3. the person watching animation movies is on the left or right of the person watching superhero movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |  4  |
| Movie-Genre   | musical | animation | superhero | spy |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-5::.
