2. the person who's sport is golf is on the right of the person who's sport is surfing##1
3. the person who's sport is basketball is on the right of the person who's sport is golf##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |    2    |  3   |     4      |
| Sport   | weightlifting | surfing | golf | basketball |

