.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-10::.
There 4 different types of food: avocado, broccoli, pumpkin, strawberry
1. the person eating broccoli is on the right of the person eating strawberry##1
2. the person eating broccoli is between the person eating avocado and the person eating strawberry##2
3. the person eating avocado is on the left or right of the person eating pumpkin##3
4. the person eating avocado is on the left or right of the person eating pumpkin##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |    2     |    3    |    4    |
| Food   | strawberry | broccoli | avocado | pumpkin |

